Query: Hoa don thang nay cua toi la bao nhieu?
SimpleSQL:
SELECT
  b.total_amount
FROM bills AS b
WHERE
  b.rental_id = (
    SELECT
      r.id
    FROM rentals AS r
    WHERE
      r.tenant_id = 'YOUR_USER_ID'
    ORDER BY
      r.created_at DESC
    LIMIT 1
  )
ORDER BY
  b.created_at DESC
LIMIT 1;

Query: Tien nha thang truoc toi tra chua?
SimpleSQL:
SELECT
  p.payment_date,
  p.amount,
  p.currency,
  p.payment_method,
  p.payment_status
FROM payments AS p
WHERE
  p.payer_id = 'YOUR_USER_ID'
  AND p.payment_date >= DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month')
  AND p.payment_date < DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE)
LIMIT 100;

Query: Phong tui co cho nuoi cho meo ko?
SimpleSQL:
SELECT
  r.id,
  r.name,
  r.description
FROM rooms AS r
LEFT JOIN room_rules AS rr
  ON r.id = rr.room_id
LEFT JOIN room_rule_templates AS rrt
  ON rr.rule_template_id = rrt.id
WHERE
  rrt.name ILIKE '%thú cưng%'
LIMIT 100;

Query: Liet ke cac khoan phi trong hoa don moi nhat.
SimpleSQL:
SELECT
  bi.item_name,
  bi.amount
FROM bills AS b
JOIN bill_items AS bi
  ON b.id = bi.bill_id
ORDER BY
  b.created_at DESC
LIMIT 100;

Query: Yeu cau dat phong cua toi o Savoy Residence duoc duyet chua?
SimpleSQL:
SELECT
  rb.id,
  rb.status
FROM room_bookings AS rb
JOIN rooms AS r
  ON rb.room_id = r.id
JOIN buildings AS b
  ON r.building_id = b.id
WHERE
  b.name = 'Savoy Residence'
  AND rb.tenant_id = 'YOUR_USER_ID'
LIMIT 100;

Query: Tim giup toi may phong tro gia duoi 3 trieu o quan Thu Duc.
SimpleSQL:
SELECT r.id, r.name, r.description, rp.base_price_monthly
FROM rooms r
JOIN buildings b ON b.id = r.building_id
JOIN districts d ON d.id = b.district_id
LEFT JOIN room_pricing rp ON rp.room_id = r.id
WHERE d.district_name ILIKE '%Thủ Đức%'
  AND r.is_active = true
  AND rp.base_price_monthly < 3000000
ORDER BY rp.base_price_monthly ASC NULLS LAST
LIMIT 100;

Query: Ai dang o phong 202, toa nha Central Park?
SimpleSQL:
SELECT u.id, u.first_name, u.last_name
FROM users u
JOIN rentals r ON u.id = r.tenant_id
JOIN room_instances ri ON r.room_instance_id = ri.id
JOIN rooms ro ON ri.room_id = ro.id
JOIN buildings b ON ro.building_id = b.id
WHERE ri.room_number = '202'
  AND b.name ILIKE '%Central Park%'
LIMIT 100;

Query: Toa nha Savoy co bao nhieu phong (phong cu the)?
SimpleSQL:

  COUNT(id)
FROM rooms
WHERE
  building_id = (
    SELECT
      id
    FROM buildings
    WHERE
      name = 'Savoy'
  )
LIMIT 100;
